=head1 Talking about Padre and wxPerl in Haifa
=timestamp 1226472178
=tags Perl, Perl 5, IDE, Perl Mongers, Haifa, Padre

As <a href="http://perl.org.il/pipermail/perl/2008-November/009887.html">announced</a> on the 
<a href="http://www.perl.org.il/mailman/listinfo/perl/">mailing list</a> of the 
<a href="http://www.perl.org.il">Israeli Perl Mongers</a> I am going to give a talk about
<a href="http://padre.perlide.org/">Padre, the Perl IDE</a> and development using 
<a href="http://wxperl.sourceforge.net/">wxPerl</a> in Haifa on the 19th of November.

That's once week from now.

It will take place in the offices of <a href="http://www.qualcomm.com/">Qualcomm</a> 
which are located in the Omega Building, at the south entrance of 
<a href="http://www.matam.co.il/">MATAM</a>, which is on the south entrance of Haifa. 
It is 15 minutes walk from the 
<a href="http://www.israrail.org.il/">train</a> / bus station <i>Hof HaCarmel</i>.

